Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.produce

Provides interfaces and classes for producing WSDL message data from BPEL activities (e.g., invoke and reply).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeMessageDataProducer Defines interface for producing outgoing message data.
IAeMessageDataProducerContext Defines the interface for a message data producer to interact with a BPEL implementation object.
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractMessageDataProducer The base class for message data producers that provides access to a delegate IAeMessageDataProducerContext.
AeActivityInvokeProducerContext Implements access to an invoke activity for a message data producer.
AeActivityReplyProducerContext Implements access to an reply activity for a message data producer.
AeEmptyMessageDataProducer Implements a message data producer that produces an empty message.
AeToPartsMessageDataProducer Implements a message data producer that copies data according to a series of toPart definitions.
AeVariableMessageDataProducer Implements a message data producer that copies data from a variable.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.wsio.produce Description

Provides interfaces and classes for producing WSDL message data from BPEL activities (e.g., invoke and reply).
